{"tid":2251812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"默克爾呼籲德國企減少對中國依賴","createTime":"2020-10-21T05:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T06:27:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc546c6a66bab532fdfd515fd984f80c5798eaa9","tid":2251812,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2370842093067110/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fphotos%2Fa.645858435565493%2F2370842093067110%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=2b3bc119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2370842093067110/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰 Nathan Law<br />\n42分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【🇩🇪德國戰線｜默克爾罕有高調呼籲德企減少對華依賴 將供應鍊分散到其他亞太地區】<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情打亂全球供應錬，加上美中貿易戰及中共最近針對外資的措施，不少公司考慮將生產線撤出中國。德國總理默克爾昨日出席德國亞太會議時，罕有呼籲德國企業須考慮將現時在大陸的生產線，分散到亞太地區其他新市場，政府會繼續提供配套。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，德國現時75%對亞洲出口集中東亞，其中一半是中國，認為亞太區有更多機遇。同場的經濟部長Peter Altmaier亦表示，德國企業必須分散投資，不要依賴單一供應鍊，並認為新加坡及南韓處理疫情不錯，相信經濟很快恢復，認為應加以利用。<br />\n<br />\n這是德國繼9月推出主張減少對華依賴的新印太戰略以來，首次由高級官員高調作出呼籲。雖然過去法國總統馬克龍亦有類似呼籲，但主要集中防疫工作上，而今次活動有不少德國企業及商會出席，政府所針對的明顯是德國整體商界的呼籲。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是，連大陸最大外商投資機構之一的西門子總裁Joe Kaeser亦表示，將視越南及印尼為重要投資選擇。不少跨國公司在越南推行大量投資，德國亦在該地培訓工人，而遷去南越亦比較容易。印尼則是中產人口持續增加，他認為德國公司及政界應如過去在中國一樣提高印尼員工技能。<br />\n<br />\n雖則德國官員強調今次不代表與中國脫鉤，只想減少依賴，「造大個餅」，惟因中國近年生產成本日漸上升，疫情及中共對其他國家的「威脅式外交」亦加大其政治、外交上的不確定性，相信生產鍊逐步「去中國化」將會是各大跨國企業的未來趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dw_chinese/status/1318201372848885760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdw_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1318201372848885760&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=a9459ea3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdw_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1318201372848885760&h=90030b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dw_chinese/status/1318201372848885760</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ABSCBNNews/status/1318466986813366275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FABSCBNNews%2Fstatus%2F1318466986813366275&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=5b55b3bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FABSCBNNews%2Fstatus%2F1318466986813366275&h=280181ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ABSCBNNews/status/1318466986813366275</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SCMPNews/status/1318325491737235456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCMPNews%2Fstatus%2F1318325491737235456&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ab00806e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCMPNews%2Fstatus%2F1318325491737235456&h=fd4b849e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SCMPNews/status/1318325491737235456</a>"},{"pid":"753ba36efd1ca4e7ec559be3c07c0e2788cf5487","tid":2251812,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"王毅去德國,&nbsp;唔係贏左咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df56cd4e7bd4c32bbc05038c2adeece31b37343a","tid":2251812,"uid":342947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"呢條共婆都歸邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2dd3348643486ee221ac6fcc1db3f4c8684f2c9","tid":2251812,"uid":121146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"德國婆講乜我都唔撚信  落台吧啦"},{"pid":"33034e8158ad76f76194230b61faf3d7717c8266","tid":2251812,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"中歐班列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64ac0d0e0e7593fd7041af2721f0c02ee7f5c64","tid":2251812,"uid":